{"tid":1855530,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街！大家唔好去呢個網買口罩！","createTime":"2020-02-01T06:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T07:01:47.000Z","uid":22122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"87b61cf37ffdd0db50ebe092b0e57ac75a01aed3","tid":1855530,"uid":22122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T06:41:25.000Z","msg":"今朝收到朋友send 呢個網黎話有口罩買，咪諗住狗衝買10盒自己用唔哂都可以幫朋友，點知一落單就發現有問題！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://avvyhealth.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Favvyhealth.com&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=15451f3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://avvyhealth.com</a><br />\n<br />\n疑點：<br />\n1）口罩買完又有貨，源源不斷，幾乎每分鐘都有人落order，但數量不跌反升 <br />\n2）再睇FAQ頁係無內容，其他類別產品係空，亦無refund、shipping&amp; return 指引 <br />\n3）公司地址有2個，一個係Taxas，但地圖又標示Seattle <br />\n4）無得用credit card，只可用PayPal，PayPal係比錢比一個GMAIL Account，如果係正式公司，應該可以用credit card<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家小心呀！可以去呢度 幫手 report 佢 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.econsumer.gov/en/FileAComplaint#crnt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.econsumer.gov%2Fen%2FFileAComplaint%23crnt&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=718e354c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.econsumer.gov/en/FileAComplaint#crnt</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwBpGof.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwBpGof.png&h=f8505091&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fEdb5PV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfEdb5PV.png&h=b0b3d024&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZaJWWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZaJWWB.png&h=d1e99e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FOZCgWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFOZCgWB.png&h=dcf37fba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dcc5ec221fe6b50fdb07f2975255d667d2a918a9","tid":1855530,"ui